
Controls:

[w] Increase Thrust
[s] Decrease Thrust
[a] Yaw Left
[d] Yaw Right
Arrow Keys:
UP: Pitch Down
DOWN: Pitch Up
LEFT: Roll Left
RIGHT: Roll Right

Particle Effects:

The particle effects are based on the example scripts distrubuted in the Ogre
SDK, and also the ParticleEditor add-on (http://www.game-cat.com/ogre/pe/docs/)

1. Exhaust behind the airplane and enemies
2. Flares lighting up the target
3. Explosion for when there is a collision
4. Smoke when the plane has crashed into the ground
5. Fireworks when a player has completed the level
